            <description><![CDATA[
<p>Design handoff fidelity pass — fixes from spec audit: menu-bar icons now 16pt (was 18); HUD idle breath corrected to scale 0.92↔1.0 + opacity 0.65↔1; HUD recording adds outward fade for the ripple feel; past caption lines fade to 35% (current speaker full weight); 0.4s easeOut fade between onboarding screens; preferences section icons bumped to 18pt and use .primary foreground.</p>
