        <item>
            <title>Dictation 2.11.1</title>
            <pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 04:00:35 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>23</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.11.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
<p>Performance fix: drops peak unified memory footprint dramatically. Calls MLX.GPU.clearCache() after every Gemma generation, in reset(), and between map-reduce summary chunks. Adds IdleReclaimer that automatically frees the loaded Gemma model after 5 min of idleness (configurable in Preferences → Cleanup → Free cleanup model after [N] minutes idle). Targets the 17.4 GB peak found in the v2.10 perf audit.</p>
            ]]></description>
